### ===========================================
### USAGE INSTRUCTIONS
### ===========================================
### 1. First, register an admin user or login with existing admin credentials
### 2. Copy the token from the login response and replace {{admin_token}} in all requests
### 3. For testing with student role, login as a student and use {{student_token}}
### 4. Replace {{user_id}}, {{club_id}}, {{event_id}}, etc. with actual IDs from responses
### 5. For file uploads, replace the file paths with actual file paths on your system
### 6. All admin routes require both authentication and admin role
### 7. Use this file in VS Code with REST Client extension or similar HTTP client tools
